source: Know this... Revenge is never a straight line.
target: Eduki ezazu argi: mendekua ez da inoiz bide erraza izan.

source: It's easy to lose your way, to be blinded by rage.
target: Erraza da bidean galtzea, haserreak itsutzea.

source: When I look into your eyes, I see nothing but a frightened, angry child.
target: Begiratzen zaitudanean, beldurtuta eta haserretuta dagoen haur bat bakarrik ikusten dut.

source: I’ll make you pay for what you did to me.
What’s going on? Who are you?
target: Zer gertatzen da? Nor zara zu?

source: I thought you said they’d put up a fight.

target: Arakatu lekua. Ez dezala inork alde egin.

source: How dare you set foot in here again.
target: Nola ausartzen zara berriz hemen agertzen.

source: You should never have come back.
Nice to see you, it’s been a while.
I’m here to finish what I started.
When I look into your eyes, I see nothing but a frightened, angry child.
target: Begiratzen zaitudanean, beldurtuta eta haserretuta dagoen haur bat bakarrik ikusten dut.

source: Get lost! Nothin’ here for you!
target: Alde! Hemen ez dago zuretzako ezer!

source: They've blocked the entrance to <DialogHighlight>the warehouse</>.
Need to find another way inside.
target: Barrura sartzeko beste bide bat bilatu beharko dut.

source: It's locked. Let’s try upstairs first.
target: Itxita dago. Proba dezagun goian lehenengo.

source: I can make it, just need a run at it.
target: Egin dezaket, abiada pixka bat behar dut

source: Sure as hell don’t look like you belong here.
target: Argi dago hau ez dela zure lekua.

source: <DialogHighlight>Junkies</>. I don’t think they'll be a problem.
target: <DialogHighlight>Jonkiak</>. Ez dut uste arazoa izango direnik.

source: Don't make me bust this damn door down!
target: Ez dut ate madarikatu hau behera bota nahi!
Ea zer nahi duen pailazo honek.

source: You do know where you are, right?
Nobody wants to see the freak, and the freak don't wanna see nobody.
target: Inork ez du xelebrea ikusi nahi, eta xelebreak ez du inor ikusi nahi.

source: Yes, get out of my way.
Looks like we've got a smartass here, guys.
target: Badirudi hemen azkar usteko bat dugula, mutilak.

source: Oh, we got ourselves a real life white knight here.
target: Hara, bizitza errealeko zapalduen babesle bat dugu hemen.

source: Let’s relieve {ListenerGender}|gender(him,her) of the contents of {ListenerGender}|gender(his,her) pockets.
target: Arindu diezaiogun daraman karga patrikak hustuz.

source: Almost done here... Last bag's on the way to you...
target: Hemen ia bukatu dugu... Azken poltsa zuregana doa...

source: Cool... Talk once we wrap this up.
target: Bikain... Hemen bukatzen dugunean hitz egingo dugu.

source: Fat fuck calls me every two seconds to check in!
target: Ergel hori bi segundoro deika dut zertan gabiltzan jakiteko!

source: While he’s sittin’ on his ass over there.
target: Bere ipurtandi hori sofan eserita duen bitartean.

source: Another jump here... I can make it.
Shame I'll have to throw you back through it.
target: Zelako pena da hortik bueltan bidali behar izatea.

source: Come on, come on! Speed this up!
I don’t wanna be late for <DialogHighlight>The Club.</>
I plan to win big tonight.
Who in the fuck are you?

target: Ez zaitezte hor gelditu! Harrapa ezazue!

source: How the fuck you get in here?
And I bet <DialogHighlight>your keys</> could have made things a lot easier.
target: Eta apostu egingo nuke zure <DialogHighlight>giltza</>k banitu bidea errazagoa litzatekeela.

source: Don't even think about it, asshole.
This little tour you've been takin' ends here and now.
target: Eman duzun bueltaxka hemen bukatuko da.

source: I’m only here for the workout.
Must have taken a wrong turn.
Ain't got much of a choice.
I'm afraid we're gonna have to fuck you up.
We have a city to deliver to!
Boss wants everything shipped out of here today!
target: Nagusiak dena gaur bidaltzea nahi du!

source: Are you deaf or somethin', asshole?
target: Gorra zara edo zer, kirten hori?

source: Honestly, it amazes me how long you've lasted in this fuckin' job.
target: Benetan, harritu egiten nau lan puta honetan horrenbeste iraun duzula ikusiteak.

source: Almost there. Need to get through that door.
target: Ia lortu dut. Ate hau gurutzatu behar dut.

source: And somebody clean this mess up!
target: Eta garbi dezala nahaspila hau norbaitek!

source: Boss said nobody gets through. <DialogHighlight>Fajar</> stays alone.
target: Nagusiak esan du ezin dela inor pasa. Utzi <DialogHighlight>Fajar</> bakean.

source: I don't think so. Only the long-haired guy visits him.
target: Ez dut uste. Ile luzedun tipoak bakarrik bisitatzen du.

source: Look, I don't know when you last saw Fajar, but he's fuckin' nuts.
target: Begira, ez dakit noiz ikusiko zenuen Fajar azkenengoz, baina burua erabat joan zaio.

source: You can't go in. Not today. Not ever.
target: Ezin zara sartu. Ez gaur. Inoiz ez.

source: I don’t care what your boss said.
target: Ez zait axola zure nagusiak esandakoa.

source: Step aside. I don’t want to have to hurt you.
target: Baztertu zaitez. Ez dizut minik eman nahi.

source: Forget about it, If you’re not on the list, you're not getting inside.
target: Ahaztu ezazu, ez bazaude zerrendan, ez zara sartuko.

source: Guys! We've got a problem here!
H-He’s with the fighters, for <DialogHighlight>The Burning</>.
Only Sean’s <DialogHighlight>Disciples</> have <DialogHighlight>passes</> to get inside.
target: Sean-en <DialogHighlight>Dizipulu</>ek bakarrik dituzte sartu ahal izateko <DialogHighlight>txartelak</>.

source: How the fuck did {ListenerGender}|gender(he,she) get here?
I’m not looking for a fight.
Neither am I. I just do computers and stuff.
target: Ezta ni ere. Ordenagailuekin aritzen naiz.

source: I need to access the locked computer of someone important.
target: Garrantzitsua den norbaiten blokeatutako ordenagailuan sartu behar dut.

source: And why should I help you?
This ‘someone important’ is the head of The Corporation.
target: 'Garrantzitsua den norbait' hori Korporazioaren burua da.

source: Really? You got some nerve going after her. I like that.
target: Benetan? Ausarta zara bere aurka joateko. Gustatzen zait.

source: Try to use this, it’ll be fun.
Because I can beat you up?
You can try this key, but I can’t promise anything.
target: Probatu giltza honekin, baina ezin dizut ziurtatu.

source: It’s cool, I don’t want any trouble.
target: Ongi da, ez dut arazorik nahi.

source: Are you a friend of Sean’s?
No. And seeing how he treats others, I don't think he has any.
target: Ez. Eta gainontzekoak nola tratatzen dituen ikusita, ez dut uste batere duenik.

source: I’m not looking for a fight.
Neither am I. I just do computers and stuff.
target: Ezta ni ere. Ordenagailuekin aritzen naiz.

source: I need to access the locked computer of someone important.
And why should I help you?
This ‘someone important’ is the head of The Corporation.
target: 'Garrantzitsua den norbait' hori Korporazioaren burua da.

source: Really? You got some nerve going after her. I like that.
target: Benetan? Ausarta zara bere aurka joateko. Gustatzen zait.

source: Try to use this, it’ll be fun.
Because I can beat you up?
You can try this key, but I can’t promise anything.
target: Probatu giltza honekin, baina ezin dizut ziurtatu.

source: It’s cool, I don’t want any trouble.
target: Ongi da, ez dut arazorik nahi.

source: I’m not looking for a fight.
Neither am I. I just do computers and stuff.
target: Ezta ni ere. Ordenagailuekin aritzen naiz.

source: Are you a friend of Sean’s?
No. And seeing how he treats others, I don't think he has any.
target: Ez. Eta gainontzekoak nola tratatzen dituen ikusita, ez dut uste batere duenik.

source: It’s cool, I don’t want any trouble.
target: Ongi da, ez dut arazorik nahi.

source: Did you think this was a pyjama party or somethin’?
target: Hau pijama festa edo horrelako zerbait zela uste zenuen?

source: Come on, show us what you can do, Kung-Fu {ListenerGender}|gender(Guy,Girl)!
target: Tira, erakutsiguzu zer egin dezakezun, Kung-Fu {ListenerGender}|gender(Mutila,Neska)!

source: Hey, didn't you hear my friend?
target: Eh, ez diozu nire lagunari entzun?

source: Alright, alright... You made your point.
The two giants over there, what’s behind their door?
target: Hango bi erraldoi horiek, zer dago ate horren atzean?

source: Tonight’s fights. And the Burning event!
target: Gaur gaueko borrokak. Eta Erreketa ikuskizuna!

source: Hey, did you hear what she just said? We’re closed for the night.
target: Aizu, entzun al duzu berak esandakoa? Gaurkoz itxi dugu jada.

source: Come on, Shen, kick his ass! I got a shit-ton of money riding on you!
target: Tira, Shen, emaiozu egurra! Sekulako dirutza jarri dut zure alde!

source: What the hell’s going on here?
Is this part of the fight or somethin’?
target: Hau borrokaren parte da edo zer?

source: Well, come on then, don’t just stand there looking at {ListenerGender}|gender(him,her).
target: Tira ba, ez zaitez berari begira gelditu.
Emaiozu ostikada bat ipurdi alu horretan!

source: Why the fuck are you only calling me back now?
Get all the money to safety, I’ll be right there...after the fights.
target: Eraman diru guztia leku segurura. Oraintxe noa... borroken ondoren.

source: You are not supposed to be part of tonight’s group.
target: Zuk ez zenuke gaur gaueko taldearen parte izan behar.

source: Let me through, I don’t want any trouble.
target: Utzi pasatzen, ez dut inolako arazorik nahi.

source: Leave me alone, I have to train.
What did you reach? I hope I’ll make it to the staff fight.
target: Zer lortu duzu? Makilen borrokara arte ailegatzea espero dut.

source: Above this door are the three trials.
target: Ate honen atzean daude hiru probak.

source: First, I want to fight all of you.
target: Hasteko, zuek guztion aurka borrokatu nahi dut.

source: Step forward. you're about to be tested.
target: Eman pausu bat aurrera. Oraintxe proban jarriko zaitugu.

source: The winner becomes the king, the loser a thief.
target: Garailea errege bihurtzen da. Galtzailea, berriz, lapurra.

source: He will drag you, and all the others, down into the abyss.
target: Zu eta gainontzeko guztiak amildegirantz eramango zaituzte.

source: Look around you. You don’t look so different to me.
target: Begiratu ingurua. Ez zara nire hain desberdina.

source: If you didn’t want to fight, why did you come this far?
target: Ez baduzu borrokatu nahi, zertarako etorri zara honaino?

source: How many trials do I still have left before meeting Sean?
target: Zenbat proba egin behar ditut Sean-ekin topo egiteko?

source: Two more challenges lay ahead: Dexterity and Endurance.
target: Bi erronka dituzu aurretik: Trebezia eta Erresistentzia.

source: But I’m afraid you’ll be too late for the final trial.
target: Baina azken probarako berandu zabiltzala uste dut.
Borroka hau oraindik ez da amaitu.

source: End of the road for you, the trial is finished.
target: Zure bidea hemen bukatzen da, proba amaitu da.

source: The Burning ceremony has begun, no outsider allowed.
target: Erreketa zeremonia hasi da, ez da kanpotarrik onartzen.

source: You’re almost as good as Yang.
I thought he was unchallenged at that old bastard’s school.
target: Uste nuen ez zuela zahar eroaren eskolan bere pareko aurkaririk.

source: Have you not figured it out by now?
Enough games, let’s put an end to this show.
target: Akabo jokoak, buka dezagun antzerki honekin.

source: A ghost from your past, here to put an end to this sideshow.
target: Zure iraganeko mamu bat, antzerki honi amaiera emateko etorria.

source: You picked the wrong person to haunt.
target: Okerreko pertsona aurrean agertu zara bada.

source: Need to find the key first.
Locked. Looks like I’ll need to go through the exhibition.
target: Itxita. Erakusteketatik pasatu behar dudala dirudi.

source: Eyes on the target in the atrium. Everyone get into position.
target: Atarian ikusi dut jomuga. Denak zuen posizioetara.

source: It was foolish of you to come here.
You’re {ListenerGender}|gender(him,her), aren’t you? You’re the one that took down Sean.
target: Zu zara, ezta? Zu zara Sean garaitu zuena.

source: He must have the card on him.
I only wish to meet her.
target: Bera ikustea besterik ez dut nahi.

source: I told you, Kuroki will not speak with you or anyone else.
target: Esan dizut, Kuroki-k ez du zurekin edo beste inorekin hitz egingo.

source: For the last time, step aside.
Nobody outruns their past. Not even her.
target: Inork ez du bere iragana ahazten. Ezta berak ere.

source: Wrong. She left this path and you won’t pull her back in!
target: Oker zaude. Berak bide hau utzi zuen eta ez duzu berriz itzultzea egingo!

source: ...  believed that if we took the time to stand outside in the rain...
target: ...  uste nuen kanpoan zutik, euritan denbora nahikoa igaroz gero...

source: ...  it would cleanse us both physically and spiritually.
Water has the power to finally set us free.
target: Urak gu aske egiteko boterea du.

source: But like the darkness itself, we must first embrace it.
target: Baina iluntasuna bera bezala, lehenengo besarkatu egin behar dugu.

source: Or the shadows of the past consume us whole.
target: Edo iraganeko itzalek erabat kontsumituko gaituzte.

source: ... it represents birth and the cleansing of a darkened soul;
target: ... ilundutako arimaren jaiotza eta garbitzea adierazten du;

source: water is the key to being reborn.
It is considered redemptive in nature...
... it floats with one-seventh of its bulk above water."
target: ... zazpiren bat besterik ez dago uraren gainetik."

source: Our consciousness is merely the tip of the iceberg.
target: Gure kontzientzia iceberg-aren punta besterik ez da.

source: We must dive beneath the waters to explore the subconscious.
target: Uretan sakon sartu behar dugu gure subkontzientea esploratzeko.

source: I know a hundred ways to kill you.
You should have run when she gave you the chance.
target: Aukera eman dizunean egin behar zenuen alde.

source: Unfortunately, I don't think you'll have that opportunity.
target: Zoritzarrez, ez dut uste aukera hori izango duzunik.

source: Don't be shy, come closer so I can get a better look at you.
target: Ez izan lotsatia, zatoz hurbilago zu hobeki ikusi ahal izateko.

source: Need to find another way down.
target: Beherako beste bide bat aurkitu behar dut.

source: Shut down all entrances and exits!
You cannot escape. You are trapped.
target: Ezin duzu ihes egin. Harrapatuta zaude.

source: ... Strike hard and fast. We must be swift and just--
target: ... Kolpatu gogor eta azkar. Honek azkarra izan behar du eta--
Etorri eta egin aurre zure epaiari.

source: Squad Seven, {ListenerGender}|gender(he,she)'s in the elevator shaft.
Send Squad Nine, send them now!
This made-up order who kept for themselves what belongs to the people.
target: Ordena inprobisatu bat besterik ez da, herriarena dena bereganatu nahi duena.

source: But truth always finds its way.
target: Baina egiak beti aurkitzen du bere bidea.

source: To each crime its punishment, and to each punishment its weapon.
target: Krimen bakoitzari bere zigorra, eta zigor bakoitzari bere arma.

source: My father never did anything wrong.
target: Nire aitak inoiz ez zuen ezer txarrik egin.

source: The only person guilty of a crime is you.
target: Krimen baten errudun bakarra zu zara!

source: There's no other way, this must be it.
target: Ez dago beste biderik, horrela izan bedi.

source: This is a place for broken bodies and spirits.
target: Leku hau puskatutako gorputz eta arimentzako da.

source: as long as they step through our door with humility and peace.
target: ate hau umiltasun eta soseguz pasatzen badute.

source: It's the highest building, just keep going up.
target: Eraikinik altuena da, igotzen jarraitzea besterik ez duzu.

source: Are you here for the cure? They say this place works miracles.
target: Sendagaiarengatik zaude hemen? Leku honek mirariak gertatzen direla diote.

source: leaves this place free of what they walked through those doors with.
target: ateak gurutzatzean zekarren zamatik aske uzten du leku hau atzean.

source: Even the ones with time no longer on their side...
target: Baita denbora beraien alde ez dutenek ere...

source: People just like you and me.
I hope you find what you're looking for.
I find that hard to believe.
Well, I did hear of people vanishing from here...
target: Tira, jendea hemendik desagertu izan dela entzun dut...

source: Maybe belief is what they lacked.
Sorry, I don't have time for this.
No time? Isn't that why we're all here?
target: Denborarik ez? Ez al gaude guztiok hemen horrexegatik?

source: These rooms are for our “special” guests.
Let me show you to yours.
I need to greet our guest.
It is an honor to meet you.
The journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.
target: Milaka kilometrotako bidaia pausu bakarrarekin hasten dira.

source: Your final test will begin here.
target: Zure azken proba hemen hasiko da.

source: To reveal the path you must truly let go.
target: Bidea ikusteko, atzean utzi behar duzu.

source: Only then will the clouds begin to lift.
target: Orduan bakarrik hasiko dira lainoak joaten.
Ekintzak hitzak baino ozenago mintzatzen dira.

source: You're a disgrace to your art.
